headline.print_headline: At Tech Fest: 3D Printers, Bitcoin and 'Titanfall'
headline.main: At Tech Fest: 3D Printers, Bitcoin and 'Titanfall'

lead_paragraph: Bitcoin, 3-D printed candy and George Takei, the Star Trek-actor-turned-Facebook-phenomenon, are among the attractions this week at the South By Southwest festival in Austin, Texas, where the geek set is slowly filing out to make room for hordes of musicians descending on the city.
